snippet.title: Amber Heard looks in good spirits as she joins lookalike sister Whitney and nephew on a shopping
snippet.description:
Amber Heard looks in good spirits as she joins lookalike sister Whitney and nephew on a shopping trip in LA

She's currently biding her time as she awaits the next hearing in her ongoing legal battle with ex-husband Johnny Depp. 

And Amber Heard was seen out shopping in Los Angeles on Friday with her sister Whitney Henriquez and nephew Hunter.

The trio were spotted in the car park of Home Depot, where they shopped for some home improvement materials and a large house plant. 

Family time: Amber Heard was seen out shopping in Los Angeles on Friday with her sister Whitney Henriquez and nephew Hunter

Amber donned a tight-fitting black top that showed off her athletic physique, which she matched with a pair of loose-fitting jeans.


For footwear, she sported a pair of white Converse trainers, while she wore a nude-coloured face mask to protect against Covid-19. 

Whitney meanwhile wore a baggy white V-neck T-shirt that she tucked into a set of heavily ripped jeans.
